# Default Hyperparameters

Use as starting values in `conf/experiment/` and overrides:

| Symbol | Parameter | Default |
| ------ | --------- | ------- |
| $B$ | Local batch size | 64 |
| $E$ | Local epochs | 5 |
| $\eta$ | Learning rate | 0.01 |
| $\rho$ | Weight decay / momentum | 0.99 |
| $\alpha$ | Dirichlet concentration | 0.1, 0.5, 10.0 |
| $C$ | Client fraction per round | 0.1 |
| $T$ | Communication rounds | 100–500 (dataset-dependent) |
